Investigating the Life Expectancy and Proteolytic Degradation of Engineered 
Skeletal Muscle Biological Machines.

Cvetkovic C(1)(2), Ferrall-Fairbanks MC(3), Ko E(1)(2), Grant L(1)(2), Kong 
