The effect of PD-L1 testing on the cost-effectiveness and economic impact of 
immune checkpoint inhibitors for the second-line treatment of NSCLC.

Aguiar PN Jr(1), Perry LA(2), Penny-Dimri J(2), Babiker H(3), Tadokoro H(4), de 
Mello RA(5), Lopes GL Jr(6).

Author information:
(1)Doctoral Grade Fellowship, Clinical Oncology Sector, Faculdade de Medicina do 
